{"title":"docker安装","uid":"30203d9cdc7458d307e82acc7bbcb96a","slug":"docker","date":"2022-05-12T04:54:24.980Z","updated":"2022-05-12T05:10:51.283Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/docker.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"docker安装\"><a href=\"#docker安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"docker安装\"></a>docker安装</h2><blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>系统版本：</li>\n</ol>\n<p>  要安装 Docker Engine，您需要 CentOS 7、CentOS 8（流）或 CentOS 9（流）的维护版本。</p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>卸载旧版本：</li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> yum remove <span class=\"token function\">docker</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n                 docker-client <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n                 docker-client-latest <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n                 docker-common <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n                 docker-latest <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n                 docker-latest-logrotate <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n                 docker-logrotate <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n                 docker-engine<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>设置存储库</li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token operator\">></span>yum <span class=\"token function\">install</span> -y yum-utils\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span>yum-config-manager <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n   --add-repo <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n   https://download.docker.com/linux/centos/docker-ce.repo<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>安装最新版doker</li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token operator\">></span>yum <span class=\"token function\">install</span> docker-ce docker-ce-cli containerd.io docker-compose-plugin -y<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>启动docker</li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token operator\">></span>systemctl start <span class=\"token function\">docker</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<ol start=\"6\">\n<li>设置开机自启</li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token operator\">></span>systemctl <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">enable</span> <span class=\"token function\">docker</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre></blockquote>\n","text":"docker安装 系统版本： 要安装 Docker Engine，您需要 CentOS 7、CentOS 8（流）或 CentOS 9（流）的维护版本。 卸载旧版本： sudo yum remove docker \\ docker-client \\ docker-client-l...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":657,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"docker","slug":"docker","count":1,"path":"api/tags/docker.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#docker%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\"><span class=\"toc-text\">docker安装</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Potter","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"www.baidu.com","description":"个人学习爱好者","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/BJPotter","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{},"next_post":{"title":"个人学习路线图","